<p>The girls of BLACKPINK were previously expected to showcase their new songs at the second half of the DEADLINE World Tour. They will resume their concerts in Kaohsiung in a couple of days, after 2 months of rest to work on their album. Recently, <a href="https://www.pinkvilla.com/entertainment/blackpink-adds-2-shows-to-deadline-world-tour-across-singapore-and-hong-kong-know-new-schedule-1397004">2 dates have been added</a> to their planned show schedule, with the tour now ending on January 26, 2026. An entire Asian leg of the tour will follow the team, with fans raising expectations for more global gigs being added eventually.</p>
