<p>Spring Day has grabbed 4 music show wins at Show Champion, M Countdown, Music Bank, and Inkigayo, where it won during its second week of release. A remix of Spring Day was released for free via SoundCloud on June 4, 2018, thanks to the popularity of the original. Meanwhile, a Japanese version of the song was dropped on May 10, 2017, as a B-side release of a single album.&nbsp;</p>

