<p>It seems that the younger ones have taken it in stride, as the oldest member, James, added, &ldquo;I think in the end, we make up CORTIS, but at the same time, the staff and everyone included - they&#39;re all part of CORTIS. It&#39;s all a big team and big family.&rdquo;</p>

