<p><strong>The full lineup of headliners goes as follows: </strong>Tyler, The Creator and Luke Combs on Thursday (July 31), Olivia Rodrigo and Korn on Friday (August 1), R&uuml;f&uuml;s Du Sol and TWICE on Saturday (August 2), and lastly, Sabrina Carpenter and A$AP Rocky on Sunday (August 3).</p>

